rows.label: xs33620100_MSG0010
rows.name: Hiya, pard! Up and at 'em, I see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33620100_MSG0020
rows.name: ...Uh, guess that's a little too cheerful, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33620100_MSG0030
rows.name: Me? Oh, I'm right as rain. Totally rarin' to go![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33620100_MSG0040
rows.name:
Say, we're headin' back, right?
I could tell by your grimace.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33620100_MSG0050
rows.name:
Don't worry, we got this.
That donkey won't get the last word.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33620100_MSG0060
rows.name: Let's get going! I've been itching to shoot something![ST:wait ]
